name: Black Trio Beaded Bracelet Set
description:
A One Of A Kind set of beaded bracelets. The beads are a variety of lava, shell, semi precious stones, vintage, resin, acai, wood and/or metal. All tassels are handmade. All feathers are handmade of leather.

Set includes: A feather leather beaded bracelet with a handmade feather, A bohemian beaded tassel bracelet with a large stone, and A single beaded bracelet with an Asian inspired large bead. Bracelets can be worn individually, as a set or mixed with other bracelets. 

Bracelets are stretchy therefore one size fits most. 
Measures approx. 7.5 inches. 
Sold as a set of 3 bracelets as pictured.
Handmade in California.
